LORRAINE
Now, the covid booster rollout-
GFX1 EXPRESS FRONT PAGE
makes the front pages this morning - with the over-40s able to book their third jabs from today.
CAM1 
Dr Hilary joins me now.
1 + 1
This is good news?

YES A MILLION PEOPLE IN THEIR 40S WILL BE OFFERED A COVID TOP-UP JAB FROM TODAY AS THE BOOSTER CAMPAIGN IS STEPPED UP. 

THERE'S A PUSH TO GET AS MANY PEOPLE BOOSTED AS POSSIBLE, 

VACCINE ULAY

THE JOINT COMMITTEE ON VACCINATION AND IMMUNISATION HAVE REVEALED THEY'RE ALREADY CONSIDERING A MOVE TO GET 18-39 YEAR OLDS OFFERED THE BOOSTER. 

OVER 15 MILLION BOOSTERS HAVE BEEN ADMINISTERED ALREADY. WE PUSHED OVER 15 MILLION OVER THE WEEKEND. 

PROFESSOR SIR ANDREW POLLARD, WHO HELPED CREATE THE OXFORD/ASTRAZENECA JAB, SUGGESTED THAT WITHOUT JABS, THE NUMBER OF DEATHS IN THE UK MIGHT BE AROUND TWICE AS HIGH, AT AROUND 300,000.

LORRAINE
I just had my booster..

AND HOW DO YOU FEEL? 

GFX1 LK BOOSTER

LORRAINE REAX

MANY PEOPLE ARE NOTICING MORE SIDE-EFFECTS, DUE TO MIXING TWO DIFFERENT VACCINES. DATA SHOWS HAVING A PFIZER BOOSTER AFTER ASTRAZENEC, WHICH THE MAJORITY OF THOSE ELIGIBLE WILL HAVE HAD, ARE HAVING WORSE SIDE-EFFECTS

SIDE-EFFECTS COULD BE FATIGUE, ACHEING, HEADACHE AND FEVER. THEY ARE NORMAL AND YOU DON'T NEED TO WORRY UNLESS THEY PERSIST. 

THE BENEFITS OF HAVING THE BOOSTER FAR OUTWEIGH THE SMALL RISK OF SIDE-EFFECTS, AS IT DRIVES PROTECTION AGAINST COVID WELL ABOVE 90%.


GFX5 PROTESTS

LORRAINE
What's happening in Europe?

CASES ARE INCREASING IN EUROPE, SO MUCH SO THAT AUSTRIA ARE BEGINNING A NATIONAL LOCKDOWN AND ARE ENFORCING VACCINATIONS FROM FEBRUARY.  IN AUSTRIA, TENS OF THOUSANDS OF PEOPLE TOOK TO VIENNA TO PROTEST. 

NOT JUST AUSTRIA. SATURDAY SAW TENS OF THROUSANDS OF PROTESTORS IN BRUSSELS IN BELGIUM TURN AGGRESSIVE, THROWING STONES AND FIREWORKS AT POLICE.

THE NETHERLANDS HAVE SEEN THREE DAYS OF RIOTING, NOT JUST AGAINST COVIDE REGULATIONS THOUGH, ALSO ANGER AT A BAN ON FIRE WORKS AT NEW YEAR'S. 

SMALLER PROTESTS HAVE ALSO TAKEN PLACE IN ZAGREB, CROATIA AND IN COPENHAGEN. 

CASES IN THE UK ARE RISING, BUT NOT SO SHARPLY AS NETHERLANDS AND AUSTRIA, ACCORIDNG TO GOVERNMENT DATA. WE'RE ON TRACK, SO LONG AS WE KEEP TO THE ADVICE. NUMBERS ARE MOVING UP, BUT WE'RE NOT FOLLOWING EUROPE IN THE SAME WAY. 

EUROPE PROTESTS ULAY

GFX5 BORIS JOHNSON

LORRAINE
Boris Johnson spotted without a mask again?

ABSOLUTELY, AND ITS FRUSTRATING, AND PROBABLY EMBARRASSING, FOR BORIS JOHNSON TO HAVE BEEN CAUGHT WITHOUT A MASK ON A TRAIN, AGAIN. AFTER CRITICISM FOR NOT WEARING A MASK AT COP26 AND AT A HOSPITAL VISIT, ON SATURDAY NIGHT HE WAS SPOTTED ON A TRAIN, AGAIN WITHOUT A MASK. 

GFX1 BORIS NO MASK TRAIN

GFX1 BORIS HOSPITAL

GFX1 BORIS COP26

IT REALLY IS IMPORTANT WE DON'T FOLLOW HIS LEAD ON THIS, AND WE CONTINUE TO MAKE A MASK. 

WE NEED TO SEE MASKS AS AN ACT OF KINDNESS, YOU'RE DOING IT FOR OTHER'S, AND IF WE ALL DO THAT ACT OF KINDNESS, THEN WE'LL ALL BE BETTER FOR IT. UNLESS YOU'RE EXEMPT OF COURSE.

body:
LORRAINE
But now, a new documentary tonight looking at Prince William and Harry's relationship with the press has reportedly upset senior royals.
BOXES OS2 SOUTH LONDON
Royal Editor Russell Myers joins us now.
The Queen's not happy?

THERE'S REPORTEDLY BEEN A FALL OUT OVER A NEW TWO-PART BBC DOCUMENTARY THAT AIRS TONIGHT. 

IT'S CALLED 'THE PRINCES AND THE PRESS' AND HAS BEEN CONDEMNED BY SENIOR ROYALS AS "TITTLE-TATTLE."

IT'S VERY HUSH HUSH - THEY HAVEN'T RELEASED ANY PROMOTIONAL FOOTAGE OF IT AT ALL-

GFX1 DOC PICTURES X2 - 2 PICS FROM DOC OF HARRY & WILLIAM YOUNGER AND NOW

ONLY THESE PICTURES OF THE BROTHERS.

THE PALACE IS REPORTEDLY ANGRY WITH THE CORPORATION WHO ARE SAID TO HAVE REFUSED THEIR REQUEST TO WATCH IT BEFORE IT GOES OUT TONIGHT. 

GFX1 QUEEN CHARLES WILL - THE TRIO

THE QUEEN, PRINCE CHARLES AND PRINCE WILLIAM HAVE REPORTEDLY THREATENED TO CARRY OUT A 'TRI-HOUSEHOLD' BOYCOTT OF THE BBC IF IT GOES AHEAD WITH THE PROGRAMME WITHOUT LETTING THEM SEE IT FIRST.

IN FACT, THE WHOLE SITUATION HAS REPORTEDLY LEFT THE 95-YEAR-OLD MONARCH "UPSET."

IT'S UNPRECEDENTED REALLY - EVEN IN THE HEIGHT OF BASHIR SCANDAL WE DIDN'T SEE THIS REACTION.

WILLIAM HARRY ULAY - AT THE STATUE UNVEILING

THE BBC SAYS THE TWO-PART PROGRAMME WILL PROVIDE "CONTEXT" FOR WILLIAM AND HARRY'S RELATIONSHIP WITH THE MEDIA.

A SPOKESMAN SAID: "THE PROGRAMME IS ABOUT HOW ROYAL JOURNALISM IS DONE AND FEATURES A RANGE OF JOURNALISTS FROM BROADCAST AND THE NEWSPAPER INDUSTRY."

BUT IT IS THOUGHT THE DOCUMENTARY WILL SUGGEST THE TWO PRINCES PLANTED SMEARS AGAINST EACH OTHER IN THE MEDIA. ACCORDING TO THE MAIL ON SUNDAY THE CAMBRIDGES AND SUSSEXES 'WENT TO WAR'.

LORRAINE
And the Queen might not be thrilled with the new series of The Crown?

I DON'T THINK SO - IN THE NEXT FEW SERIES WE WILL SEE IMDELDA STAUNTON ACTING OUT A VERY CHALLENGING TIME IN THE QUEEN'S LIFE - HER 1992 ANNUS HORNBILLS. 

QUEEN 1992 SPEECH ULAY - QUEEN MAKING SPEECH IN 1992

THAT YEAR THE QUEEN FAMOUSLY MADE A SPEECH COINING THE TERM TO DESCRIBE A YEAR WHICH SAW A FIRE AT WINDSOR, THE BREAKDOWN OF CHARLES AND DIANA'S MARRIAGE, THE FERGIE TOE-SUCKING DEBACLE AND ANNE'S DIVORCE.

GFX1 IMEDLA - AS THE QUEEN

GFX1 QUEEN IMELDA SPLIT - THE QUEEN IN 1992 AND IMELDA 

AND WE'VE SEEN FRESH PICTURES OF IMELDA IN A SIMILAR OUTFIT TO WHAT WORE THE QUEEN WORE FOR THAT MEMORABLE SPEECH AT THE GUILDHALL IN THE CITY OF LONDON.

LORRAINE
Meanwhile Camilla has been working on her look?

CAMILLA CHARLES TOUR ULAY - IN FRONT OF THE PYRAMIDS IN EGYPT

YES SO SHE APPEARS TO BE RAISING HER PUBLIC PROFILE AS WE SAW ON CHARLES AND CAMILLA'S ROYAL TOUR OF EGYPT AND JORDAN JUST LAST WEEK WHERE THEY CARRIED OUT OVER 30 ENGAGEMENTS, SOME OF WHICH WERE SOLO ENGAGEMENTS FOR THE DUCHESS.

IN LIGHT OF THIS CAMILLA SEEMS TO HAVE  MADE SOME KEY LIFE-STYLE CHANGES.

GFX1 CAMILLA FIT BIT - CAMILLA OUT AND ABOUT AT THE WEEKEND

GFX1 FITBIT CU - ZOOMED IN ON HER CUFF/WATCH

SHE HAS A BRAND NEW HAIRDRESSER AND HAS BEEN PICTURED WEARING HER FIT BIT WATCH AGAIN OVER THE WEEKEND - SHE'S DEFINITELY KEEPING AN EYE ON HER WELL-BEING AS SHE TAKES ON MORE ROYAL DUTIES.

IT'S GOOD TO SEE HER KEEPING FIT - SHE PREVIOUSLY REVEALED HOW SHE HAD BEEN TRYING BALLET WITH A GROUP OF OTHER OVER 50S (DUBBED THE SILVER SWANS) DURING THE LOCKDOWN. SHE ALSO SAID THAT SHE DOES A 'BIT' OF YOGA AND PILATES.

GFX1 CAMILLA MOSQUE - CAMILLA DOING ROYAL DUTIES IN PINK TUNIC

AND YOU CAN TELL - IN A MOSQUE IN CAIRO EVERYONE WAS COMMENTING ON HOW GLAM SHE LOOKED.

LORRAINE 
We're going to be seeing more of Camilla?

CAMILLA ULAY - CAMILLA DOING ROYAL DUTIES MEETING CARRIE AND MAKING SPEECH

YES - IN FACT LORRAINE CAMILLA WILL PLAY A LEADING PART IN THE QUEEN'S PLATINUM JUBILEE NEXT YEAR.

SHE WILL HOST BRITAIN'S STREET PARTY - 'THE BIG LUNCH' - WHERE THOUSANDS WILL GET TOGETHER ON OUR STREETS TO CELEBRATE THE MONARCH'S 70 YEAR REIGN.

CAMILLA TAKING ON THIS ROLE IS A SIGN OF THINGS TO COME AS HER ROYAL RESPONSIBILITIES GROW - STEPPING FORWARD AS THE QUEEN STEPS BACK.

LORRAINE
There's a Royal comeback on the cards?

PROP: BATTENBURG CAKE - RUSSELL AND LK BOTH HAVE ONE

YES LORRAINE THE BATTENBERG CAKE IS MAKING A ROYAL COMEBACK 150 YEARS ON.

IT WAS ORIGINALLY WAS ORIGINALLY SAID TO HAVE BEEN PRODUCED FOR THE 1884 WEDDING OF QUEEN VICTORIA'S GRANDDAUGHTER PRINCESS VICTORIA, TO A GERMAN PRINCE, LOUIS OF BATTENBERG. BUT IT'S SET TO MAKE A COMEBACK FOR THE QUEEN'S JUBILEE NEXT YEAR.

GFX1 BATTENBERG - THE CAKE

ACCORDING TO A RECENT SURVEY, THE MARZIPAN-COVERED CAKE IS SET TO TAKE CENTRE STAGE IN NEXT YEAR'S FESTIVITIES, ALONG WITH THE VICTORIA SPONGE, BRITAIN'S FAVOURITE CAKE.

INDUSTRY EXPERTS HAVE ALSO SEEN A RISE IN THE SALE OF BATTENBERG CAKE TINS.

IT'S OBVIOUSLY A GERMAN CAKE SO IT'S RESURGENCE IN 2022 IS A FITTING TRIBUTE TO PRINCE PHILIP WHO CAN'T CELEBRATE THIS MILESTONE WITH THE QUEEN.

LORRAINE
The Queen was at the Royal christening yesterday?

GFX1 QUEEN AT CHRISTENING - PAPPED IN CAR

THE QUEEN WASN'T PROPERLY PICTURED YESTERDAY -  BUT WE DO HAVE THIS PAP SHOT OF HER TRAVELLING TO THE CHRISTENING AND I CAN CONFIRM THAT SHE WAS PRESENT AT ZARA TINDALL AND PRINCESS EUGENIE'S JOINT CHRISTENING FOR THEIR ROYAL BABIES YESTERDAY.

IT WAS HELD AT THE ROYAL CHAPEL OF ALL SAINTS IN WINDSOR GREAT PARK .

GFX1 AUGUST LUCAS SPLIT - THE TWO FAMILIES

PRINCESS EUGENIE'S FIRST CHILD AUGUST WAS CHRISTENED, ALONG WITH ZARA'S THIRD CHILD LUCAS. 

AUGUST'S CEREMONY WAS PLANNED FOR JULY BUT HAD TO BE RE-SCHEDULED DUE TO THE PANDEMIC.

IT'S  BELIEVED THIS OCCASION WILL BE THE FIRST TIME TWO ROYALS HAVE BEEN CHRISTENED TOGETHER IN THIS WAY - LOVELY TO SEE AS EUGENIE AND ZARA GET ON SO WELL.

GFX1 PRINCE PHILIP - PHILIP

BOTH COUPLES CHOSE TO GIVE THEIR SONS THE MIDDLE NAME PHILIP, IN TRIBUTE TO THE BOYS’ GREAT-GRANDFATHER PRINCE PHILIP WHO DIED IN APRIL, JUST A FEW WEEKS AFTER THEY WERE BORN.

GFX1 QUEEN PHILIP - THE COUPLE

THIS WOULD HAVE BEEN AN ESPECIALLY NICE TOUCH AS THIS WEEKEND WOULD HAVE ALSO MARKED THE QUEEN AND PHILIP'S 74TH WEDDING ANNIVERSARY.

LORRAINE THANKS
